### Token Introspection
POST {{auth-url}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token/introspect
Authorization: Basic {{intro-client-id}} {{intro-client-secret}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept: application/json

